	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=202137><span id= >Culliganator</span></a><br><span id=notbold>7 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>It means you can take this item and combine in with one of your items.<br><br>Basically you look at the restrictions info on the stone, and then combine this stone with a piece of your equipment that falls into a category within the restrictions.<br><br>You combine the items at a wayfarer camp's bird feeder.&nbsp;&nbsp;The stone disappears and the item is returned to you with the stat associated with the stone.<br><br>Its important to note the item becomes no drop so the best thing to do is to augment your no drop items first.</p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
